{
  "texts": [
    "Quotas used to sample vignettes that are representative of symptom clusters typically entered in SAA based on a previous study on symptom distributions 37.",
    "Following best practices to reduce effects from inputter variability, data from SAAs were collected by two graduate students (DS and SZ) -without professional medical training -who entered the cases into different SAAs between October 24 th 2023 and January 22 nd 2024.",
    "Having students enter the vignettes rather than health professionals ensured that only information stated in the vignettes were entered without subjective clinical interpretation of symptoms, which could introduce bias 17.",
    "The two students entered each vignette into 12 different SAAs (amounting to 540 assessments).",
    "The selection of SAAs was based on our comparator dataset 13 to ensure comparability."
  ]
}